		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">With a forceful word and a wave of your hand, you clear the air, literally and figuratively.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">All aerosol and particulate contaminants and hazards such as poisonous gas, steam, smoke, disease, and even pollen and foul smells are instantly purged from the spell&rsquo;s area. Creatures suffering ill effects from a purged contaminant immediately gain another saving throw, ending the effect on a success. In addition, creatures suffering from effects causing them to be charmed, confused, or frightened also gain a new saving throw against the effect, ending it on a success.</p>",
